{"tid":494103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田站跳軌死者證實為中大中國學生","createTime":"2017-12-09T09:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T05:41:33.000Z","uid":39464,"like":495,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"ea62b2795eaf909a22c9c8ff75605d6c613c1824","tid":494103,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171209/large/1512790893_8251.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171209%2Flarge%2F1512790893_8251.jpg&h=1baa0597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【14:20更新】港鐵回覆<br />\n【13:20更新】死者21歲，是中大學生，內地人，有情緒病紀錄<br />\n【12:35】墮軌男子與母親同行，事發時目擊兒子突然跳軌，事後傷心激動要送院<br />\n<br />\n上午10時50分，一名男子在沙田站北行月台墮軌，並遭一輛駛至列車輾過，重傷被困列車底，港鐵職員發現報警求助。救援人員接報到場，將男子救出移離路軌，但證實當場死亡。受事件影響，列車服務一度受阻，職員安排乘客轉搭其他列車；由於沙田站有多條路軌，列車服務很快回復正常。<br />\n警方稱死者21歲，初步調查懷疑他趁列車埋站時跳落路軌，結果遭撞到。現場沒有遺書，據了解事主有情緒病。<br />\n港鐵回覆稱，沙田站職員目擊有乘客跌落二號月台(往羅湖)，即時按動緊急掣停止列車進出，當時正有一列車抵達此月台，車長即時煞停及通知控制中心，由控制中心報警。該列車上的乘客要落車，到對面月台轉乘另一列車。至11時20分，消防將該男子移離路軌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171209/57559706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171209%2F57559706&d=Cm8rMD9sWM3SSTfCICCbrDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=7e249291\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171209%2F57559706&h=f4158f74\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171209/57559706</a>"},{"pid":"1f7e5012327e2e7dce9fadc81a36a1ff4bd2a99d","tid":494103,"uid":147871,"like":38,"dislike":180,"score":-142,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:04:42.000Z","msg":"Rip <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df138fbc64e8098984dab666af287f61dcd76c8","tid":494103,"uid":76216,"like":127,"dislike":29,"score":98,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:05:30.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"fc0d56db908a76ec5c425af79ff2e9595e0bbdcf","tid":494103,"uid":17859,"like":245,"dislike":7,"score":238,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:06:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171209/large/1512790893_8251.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171209%2Flarge%2F1512790893_8251.jpg&h=1baa0597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【14:20更新】港鐵回覆<br />\n【13:20更新】死者21歲，是中大學生，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">內地人</span></strong></span>，有情緒病紀錄<br />\n【12:35】墮軌男子與母親同行，事發時目擊兒子突然跳軌，事後傷心激動要送院<br />\n<br />\n上午10時50分，一名男子在沙田站北行月台墮軌，並遭一輛駛至列車輾過，重傷被困列車底，港鐵職員發現報警求助。救援人員接報到場，將男子救出移離路軌，但證實當場死亡。受事件影響，列車服務一度受阻，職員安排乘客轉搭其他列車；由於沙田站有多條路軌，列車服務很快回復正常。<br />\n警方稱死者21歲，初步調查懷疑他趁列車埋站時跳落路軌，結果遭撞到。現場沒有遺書，據了解事主有情緒病。<br />\n港鐵回覆稱，沙田站職員目擊有乘客跌落二號月台(往羅湖)，即時按動緊急掣停止列車進出，當時正有一列車抵達此月台，車長即時煞停及通知控制中心，由控制中心報警。該列車上的乘客要落車，到對面月台轉乘另一列車。至11時20分，消防將該男子移離路軌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171209/57559706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171209%2F57559706&d=Cm8rMD9sWM3SSTfCICCbrDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=7e249291\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171209%2F57559706&h=f4158f74\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171209/57559706</a></blockquote><br />\n祖國教育咁好<br />\n點解要嚟香港讀呢？"},{"pid":"56eff5881bef96ec05a3f23e61bebbdf0a9bd0ed","tid":494103,"uid":3457,"like":38,"dislike":3,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:11:34.000Z","msg":"中國又送大禮 <br />\n搞到國家亂曬"},{"pid":"bbb85dfc4b0fb5e8701db978c546e109367c470e","tid":494103,"uid":64948,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:13:31.000Z","msg":"唔抵可憐"